title: Barbie - The Greatest Lie Ever Told
description:
Wow, talk about misdirection! The trailers and advertising painted the new Barbie movie, with Margot Robbie and Ryan Gosling, as a fun, family friendly comedy. What it actually turned out to be is... well, something very different.
